content: LIST ON P2B SOON        TERMS AND CONDITIONS1. Join Aussie Digital Telegram Group & Announcement2. Bounty Manager and Team has the right to make changes to the provisions at any time.3. If you have any questions or complaints Please ask your bounty-related questions with the Bounty Manager or fill out the Complaint Form.4. Every Tiktok participants obligatory to report their work on the form provided.5. Participant is forbidden to duplicate other people's works.6. By agreeing to participate in this bounty, you acknowledge that the Username Aussie Digital you submitted is final and can't be changed.7. Bounty Manager is under no obligation to send your bounty reward and may, at its discretion, cancel your participationfrom each ongoing bounty if the participant does not follow the rules mentioned on this bounty thread.8. Participating in this bounty campaign or investing in it will be at your own risk.9. Talking about the bounty in the project chat group will lead to immediate disqualification from the campaign and an instant ban from the company chat group.10. KYC is not required for the bounty campaign. However, the project's team has the right to require KYC for suspicious cases.11. Please note that any offensive or inappropriate behavior will lead to immediate disqualification from the campaign.12. Using multiple accounts, cheating, and spamming are not allowed.Note: "Bounty Manager has escrowed and guarantees the reward distribution of this bounty."Proof Of Registration Post Format:Code:#PROOF OF REGISTRATIONForum Username:Forum Profile Link:Telegram Username:Chatezy Username:Username/id Aussie Digital: BOUNTY ALLOCATIONTiktok : 100%=========================================BOUNTY DURATIONBounty Program will last for 1 MonthWeek 1 : Jan 28 - Feb 03, 2023 Week 2 : Feb 04 - 10, 2023Week 3 : Feb 11 - 17, 2023Week 4 : Feb 18 - 28, 2023and will run until February 28th, 2023.BOUNTY SPREADSHETRewards:1. Have more than 10 views: 1 stake2. Have more than 100 views: 2 stakes3. Have more than 2000 views: 3 stakes4. Have more than 5,000 views: 4 stakes5. Have more than 10,000 views: 5 stakes6. Have more than 50,000 views: 10 stakesRules:  1. Participants must have at least 10 Followers.2. Each participant can send maximum 2 videos per week.3. Video Content must focus on a relevant topic: project features, project platforms, Tokensale, latest token updates, blockchain, etc.4. Only original video content will be accepted.5. Face cam video will be highly recommended and considered.6. Bot voices will not be rewarded. But, a good quality animation video with bot voices will be rewarded.7. Poor quality video will not be rewarded. Stakes will be awarded based on the number of engagements and quality.8. Videos should never be removed, Removal/deletion will result in disqualification.9. All videos need to have the project's website (www.aussiedigital.io).10. Participants must use #Aussiedigital #Tradezy #Tradedo #Chatezy #AUD #Cryptocurrency hashtags in every video.11.
